home_and_garden.title: Home & Garden
home_and_garden.description: DIY, green thumbs, and fun projects - these shows will make home improvement a little more entertaining.

561810.title: Small Is Beautiful: A Tiny House Documentary
561810.description: Discover both the advantages and drawbacks of the tiny house lifestyle with four homeowners who set out to invest in the niche market.

603179.title: Do More With Less
603179.description: Estudiantes de arquitectura ponen manos a la obra en en proyectos reales que están transformando la forma de eregir estructuras en pro de la sociedad.

627407.title: Float: The Rose Parade
627407.description: Members of the all-volunteer Burbank Tournament of Roses Association compete in the world-famous Pasadena Tournament of Roses on New Year's Day.

633781.title: The Designer Within
633781.description: Six competing interior designers are given blank canvases of brand-new, empty luxury apartments that they must transform into trendy urban spaces.

661526.title: Plant This Movie
661526.description: Exploring the zeitgeist of urban farming, Plant This Movie profiles communities of farmers in a diverse range of cities around the world.

0300006984.title: Disaster Decks
0300006984.description: Disaster Decks helps homeowners re-build their backyard disasters.

0300008157.title: Container Masters
0300008157.description: Shipping containers are turned into beautiful homes and building projects, as the Container Master team brings their clients' unique dreams to life.

02329.title: Dream Build
02329.description: Dream Build is an interstitial series that explores the personal stories of Australians who have pushed the design brief to the limit and beyond, in pursuit of building the home of their dreams.

0746.title: Wealthy Manor
0746.description: Wealthy Manor is a half-hour excursion into fine homes and fine living. Sumptuous photography and exciting music guide us through lovely rooms, elegant furnishings, and unique interior designs, showcasing the lifestyle of the wealthy.

0300007943.title: My Dream Derelict Home
0300007943.description: When renovator Simon O'Brien encounters homes that are falling apart, he provides the owners with helpful instructions to transform their houses.

03018.title: The House That 100K Built
03018.description: An architect and a design critic help stressed-out property owners, struggling to build their dreams homes on a bargain basement budget.

03912.title: Celebrity House Hunting
03912.description: Get your celebrity real estate peek on as the rich and famous show their current homes and tour even more amazing homes available on the market.

0917.title: First Homes
0917.description: Buying your first house is one of lifes biggest moments, but in the UKs tough current economic climate for first time buyers its never been tougher.

0300000063.title: The Green House Effect
0300000063.description: A factual entertainment series that visits eco-friendly buildings in South Africa to examine their designs, inspiration and development challenges.

0300009588.title: Fantasy Homes by the Sea
0300009588.description: In this lifestyle reality television series, various couples from different walks of life search for their perfect fantasy homes by the sea.

03016.title: The Restoration Man
03016.description: Architect George Clarke helps anxious homeowners restore and convert neglected historical properties into totally unique dream homes.

0511.title: Location, Location, Location
0511.description: Hosts Kirstie Allsopp and Phil Spencer entertain and provide humor, as they take house hunters to visit properties that meet their unique needs.

01725.title: Build a New Life in the Country
01725.description: British adventurers strive to pursue their dream lifestyle and home in their dream location.

02929.title: The Really Big Flip
02929.description: Three teams are competing on The Really Big Flip - a high-risk house flipping competition. The teams are hunting for the perfect property, anxious to find the worst house on the best street. But what does it really take to find, fix and flip a house?

03098.description: Historical building surveyor Marianne Suhr tours the country looking for the most exciting, unusual and traditional restoration projects. With her priceless advice for the owners and hands-on attitude, Marianne will be making repairs to crumbling castle walls, mixing up some building mud and even dabbling in a bit of dowsing in her mission to give Britain's rich architectural heritage the treatment it deserves.

02370.title: This Old House
02370.description: This Old House is the No. 1 home enthusiast brand, offering trusted information and expert advice through award-winning television

02369.title: Ask This Old House
02369.description: Ask This Old House solves the steady stream of home improvement problems faced by our viewers—and we make house calls!

03019.title: The House That 100K Built: Tricks of the Trade
03019.description: With design dilemmas galore and life savings at stake, Kieran and Piers come to the rescue of inexperienced owners building homes from scratch.

0300010391.title: Animal Cribs
0300010391.description: Antonio Ballatore and his team of designers convert ordinary living spaces into dream homes, each one unique and tailored to pets and their owners.

0906.title: My Flat Pack Home
0906.description: Amanda Lamb continues her mission to look at prefabricated properties in a completely different light, as she explores a startling array of designs.

03102.title: Best Laid Plans
03102.description: Architectural Designer Charlie Luxton and Property Developer Sophie Morgan are joining forces to help home improvers. But with so much at stake almost half of those undertaking these ambitious projects can't agree on the improvements they're making. Charlie and Sophie will be offering advice and ensuring these remarkable renovations deliver the stunning new homes their owners are dreaming of.

04018.title: Makeover Wish
04018.description: It's a lucky weekend for well-deserving people selected for a 72-hour surprise weekend getaway while top designers give them $25,000 room makeovers.

03877.title: Build a New Life in the Country Revisits
03877.description: From a grand barn to a Victorian water tower, catch up with how modest families from the U.K. who left the city for countryside charms are doing now.

0300009253.title: Find & Design
0300009253.description: A show that explores the world of multimillion-dollar homes and demonstrates to the viewer how to recreate these unique designs in their own home.

0843.title: Designing Spaces
0843.description: Go beyond simple fixes with this wide-ranging home improvement series that explores home security, mortgage tips and so much more.

04053.title: Grow Cook Eat
04053.description: Did you know you can grow vegetables and fruit in a very small garden or apartment? This series makes creating healthy food accessible to all.

0300007736.title: Save Lullingstone Castle

0300007614.title: Mundo Casa
0300007614.description: Los pasos para comprar casa en EE.UU., remodelar y decorar tu hogar, llegan en Mundo Casa, el show para quienes sueñan con casa propia.

0300010134.title: Tiny Garden
0300010134.description: Looking to transform your home into a botanic wanderlust? In this series, architects and designers share their gardening wisdom and personal journeys.

0300007570.title: Room to Improve: Dermot’s Home
0300007570.description: Dermot Bannon, one of Ireland’s most renowned architects, accepts his most personal job yet - creating his own family’s dream home.

0300009587.title: Amazing Spaces: Shed of the Year
0300009587.description: This reality series looks at one of the symbols of British eccentricity: the humble garden shed, a hallowed land of splendid isolation.

01707.title: Opening Soon By Design
01707.description: From large enterprises such as American Apparel to a mom and pop Vespa retailer, this series follows designer-architects - and the entrepreneurs who hire them - on their perilous journey from blueprint to opening day of a new business.

0300006535.description: Britain’s top chefs vie for the chance to cook at a prestigious Taste of Summer banquet, celebrating 140 years of the iconic Wimbledon Championships.

0300009656.title: Home Diagnosis
0300009656.description: Home performance experts utilize cutting edge diagnostic testing and methods to help solve mysterious issues across America in homes of all ages.

0300006121.title: House Poor
0300006121.description: A lifestyle series where homeowners with financial struggles get to reign in their financial issues while also receiving a makeover on their home.

03843.title: Honey, I Bought the House
03843.description: Reality-TV series about 9 couples who receive a deposit on a home. They are separated while one has to secure a new home in 3 weeks or lose the cash.

0300009010.description: Business gets personal, as a boyfriend and girlfriend who split up, but still work together, buy, refurbish, and sell high-end properties in Indiana.

04137.description: Top Million Dollar Agent is a reality television show that showcases the best in luxury real estate around the world. Each episode features a couple looking to invest in a knockout property, aided by a cast of top Toronto real estate agents. After touring three multi-million dollar properties, the couple has to choose which home is the perfect fit. Luckily, they have the help of not only the all-star agents but also of featured special guests that include mortgage brokers, lawyers, builders and consultants.

0300010314.title: Buying the Bayou
0300010314.description: This reality series follows people as they look to purchase property on the Bayou, a location whose real estate is outside of the norm.

0300010322.title: Buying the Rockies
0300010322.description: This reality series follows people as they search for the forever home of their dreams in the majestic beauty of the Rocky Mountains.

03020.title: Restoration Home
03020.description: Forgotten old buildings are returning to life across Britain, as ambitious owners renovate these historical gems into stunning new homes.

0300006185.title: Flip for Profit
0300006185.description: Follow a charismatic real estate tycoon as he takes broken homes and turns them around for a tidy profit to the delight of satisfied homeowners.

03829.title: Grin and Build It
03829.description: In this home renovation series, couples face a major test as they renovate their home, with one catch - it's got to be done in three days.

03252.title: Room to Improve
03252.description: Architect Dermot Bannon tests his skills as a designer and a diplomat as he tries to make clients' dream homes a reality in this renovation series.

0300007458.description: Join realtor Sarah Richardson, as she advises buyers on how to hunt for a home that’s not only affordable, but offers real potential for renovation.

03415.description: Couples compete to renovate rundown buildings into upscale apartments, and auction them for the highest price to receive a huge cash prize.

0775.title: To Build Or Not To Build

0300006992.description: Kate Bliss and her squad of antique dealers help homeowners choose between sentimental attachment and big money offers for their prized possessions.

04728.title: Today's Builder
04728.description: Builders and homeowners display the most luxurious homes in the United States in this showcase of the finest custom builders in the country.

0824.title: Building Bryks
0824.description: Watches the Bryk family fight their way through a construction nightmare so they can finally build their dream home.

02273.title: The Big Flip
02273.description: Renovators take on the challenge of fixing and flipping as many houses as they can in just 12 months or lose their minds and shirts trying.

04225.title: Double Your House for Half the Money

0300008498.title: HOMEMade

0300005945.title: Today's Homeowner With Danny Lipford
0300005945.description: If you need help with home improvements, contractor Danny Lipford has you covered with practical advice and inspiration to upgrade your abode.

04563.title: Great Taste No Money
04563.description: Ordinary people with no budget for refreshed home design get great makeovers through common sense do’s and don’ts, shopping trips and more.

0300010445.title: Weird Homes
0300010445.description: A Canadian series about some of the most unusual and bizarre homes, and the fascinating and inspiring people who built and live in them.

0300000144.title: My Bungalow Bliss
0300000144.description: Four first-time bungalow homeowners, paired with four innovative architects, are desperately seeking a solution to their dark, damp, and dated homes.

0300008694.title: Design Match
0300008694.description: Two novice design teams compete in this lifestyle series to re-create a high-end style designer room on a fraction of the original budget.

04095.title: Dermot Bannon's Incredible Homes
04095.description: A world-famous architect takes viewers on a tour of remarkable homes and the people behind them, from Australia to Sweden and Ireland.

0825.title: Building Family
0825.description: A six-part docu-drama that follows Piero and his family as he tries to fill his father's construction shoes by building a house.

03416.title: Reno Rumble
03416.description: In just one week, expert renovators transform modest houses into jaw-dropping dream homes, to make a difference in the lives of deserving homeowners.

01808.title: Homes By Design
01808.description: This unique television series features some of the most extraordinary homes from across North America and Europe.

03693.title: Spaced Out
03693.description: Experience the most imaginative and spectacular rooms ever built inside a home, from a Star Wars basement to an underwater living room.

0300006918.title: Cabin Truckers
0300006918.description: Follow the incredible exploits of a family and their business, that hauls colossal cabins and massive mansions to remote, picturesque locations.

03494.title: Nick Knowles: Original Home Restoration
03494.description: In each episode, lucky homeowners take on the huge task of remodeling their dwelling while a historian digs into the history of the house.

0300007014.title: Reno My Reno

04230.description: An energetic team of house-flipping professionals race against time to help buyers of new homes sell their old houses so they can move in soon.

01726.description: 26 contestants compete to become the head renovator of six run-down houses in the suburbs of Sydney, with challenges and eliminations as they progress.

0300005255.description: Follow amateur and professional property flippers addicted to the thrill of the flip. But will it be a successful flip or a disastrous flop?

0300007040.title: Home of the Year Ireland

0300009586.description: In each episode 3 gardens will be explored and appraised while the owners share their passion with their peers.

0300000141.title: Dr Eva’s Great Portuguese Escape
0300000141.description: Eva and Wyatt Orsmond pack up their lives in Ireland to pursue their dream of converting an old Portuguese farmhouse into a health and wellness hotel.

0300005122.description: A series focused on the stunning scenery and visual splendor of four British gardens that were created and designed during separate historical eras.

0300010315.title: Bahamas Life
0300010315.description: In this reality series, homebuyers take a break from city life and bring their island living dreams to life by searching for a place in the Bahamas.

03263.description: The Design Doctors are on a mission to help ordinary homeowners banish beige, create space and inject some imagination into their homes without breaking the bank. From high-end homes to luxury hotels these designers push the boundaries to create unique, bold and distinctive designs every time.

04229.description: A show that proves that huge home makeovers really can be done on the tiniest budget, as an interior designer shows tricks, bargains and more.

0300009573.title: Design for You
0300009573.description: Top designers provide decor tips, redesigns and creative inspiration on how to reimagine your own dream home on a budget that suits you.

03021.title: The Restoration Man Best Builds
03021.description: Architect George Clark, no stranger to ambitious renovation projects, chooses his all-time favorite buildings from his home improvement series.

03008.title: Glorious Garden's From Above
03008.description: Get a bird's eye view of Britain's most magnificent gardens, as host Christine Walkden embarks on a hot-air balloon journey across the countryside.

03634.title: Getting the Builders In
03634.description: Three pairs of builders go head to head, competing to make homeowners' dreams come true on both price and design in this British series.

0300008505.title: Landscape Artist of the Year Canada
0300008505.description: Professional and amateur landscape artists compete for a $10,000 prize and a chance to display their work at the McMichael Canadian Art Collection.

0300009466.title: The Good Life
0300009466.description: For Britain's city dwellers, the lure to exchange the daily grind for an English country living is excellent; this series follows those who have.

0300000001.title: Humble Home Hunters
0300000001.description: Humble Home Hunters takes you on a journey across Canada as new homebuyers with budgets of around $150,000 search for their dream homes.

0300005093.title: My Design Rules
0300005093.description: Three competing duos have less than two weeks to design a room before being judged by a panel of experts who can only recognize one winning team.

From gorgeous getaways in exotic places to party houses with expensive toys, this is a world of serious house envy.

04276.description: Travel around scenic New Zealand, as couples, families, and friends buy their first home, amid the country's challenging property market.

03528.title: Full Frontage
03528.description: Real estate guru Mike Pero and top landscape designer Justin Newcombe join forces to fix up the frontage of homes and transform their market value.

0300008009.title: Landscape Artist of the Year
0300008009.description: A British competition series that tasks dozens of gifted landscape artists across the UK with painting some of the country’s most spectacular scenery.
